            eTRIKS is a collaborative project focused on increasing the efficiency of translational research by:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Reducing the cost of translational research data & knowledge management</li>
            <li>Enabling non-statisticians to perform exploratory analyses</li>
            <li>Facilitating cross study analyses</li>

        </ul>

